8 An Act relating to retirement; amending 11 O.S. 2021,
Section 50-115, as last amended by Section 7, Chapter
9 151, O.S.L. 2023 (11 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 50-
115), which relates to the Oklahoma Police Pension
